# API Patterns

## HTTP Client
- Use typed fetch wrapper
- All responses typed with TypeScript interfaces
- Centralized error handling

## Authentication
- JWT in httpOnly cookie (not localStorage)
- Refresh token rotation
- Auto-logout on 401

## Data Fetching
- Use TanStack Query for caching
- Loading states via Suspense or explicit
- Optimistic updates for better UX